# Force LF line endings for all text files — prevents CRLF churn on Windows
# (the kite-mcp-server arc hit repeated CRLF/LF flips during cross-platform
# development; pin from the start to avoid the same issue here.)
* text=auto eol=lf

# Explicit binary types (no line-ending conversion)
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
*.pdf binary
*.zip binary
*.tar binary
*.gz binary
*.exe binary
*.dll binary
*.so binary
*.dylib binary
*.db binary
*.sqlite binary
